Epitome
---------

Epitome is a simple static site generator in ruby and [sinatra](http://www.sinatrarb.com/). Its readily deployable into [heroku](http://www.heroku.com/).

Dependencies:
-------------
1. [Sinatra](http://sinatrarb.com)
2. [RDiscount](http://github.com/rtomayko/rdiscount)

***

Installation:
-------------
To run it in your local machine:

*	Install Rdiscount gem (gem install rdiscount)
*	Just download the github repository and run "ruby app.rb"

To deploy in heroku:
*	cd to the directory and run "heroku create"
*	run "git push heroku"
*	run "heroku open"
*	There you go, its now deployed in heroku

